OL,3,CSecretary of State Hilary Benn sacked
OL,5,FNorthern Ireland secretary Hilary Benn
OL,6,Fhas announced he is leaving the role.
OL,8,FIn a statement on the social media
OL,9,Fplatform X, Mr Benn said: "It has been
OL,10,Fa great privilege to serve as
OL,11,FSecretary of State for Northern
OL,12,FIreland and to work with the many
OL,13,Fwonderful people I have met over the
OL,14,Flast 2 years.
OL,16,F"I wish my successor all the very best
OL,17,Fin working with the Executive to
OL,18,Fprotect stability, continuing to
OL,19,Fgenerate growth and investment and in
OL,20,Ftaking forward the Troubles Bill which
OL,21,Fis so important for so many families.
